description: Professional architectural blueprint for a 2 Acres house with For a 2BHK home on a 2-acre plot in New Delhi with a budget of INR 2,300,000, the floor plan should prioritize efficient use of space while maintaining comfort and functionality. It should include two well-ventilated bedrooms, one or two bathrooms, a compact living room, a kitchen with utility space, and a small dining area. Optimize natural light and airflow, possibly incorporating a small veranda or balcony. Given the ample land, the design can be single-story with provisions for future expansion. Use cost-effective materials and smart layout to stay within budget while ensuring livability and modern aesthetics.. Top-down 2D floor plan with precise measurements, clean lines, labeled rooms, doors, windows, and dimensions. Technical architectural drawing style with blue lines on white background.
